                                                                                                                <comments>
                            <comment id="13171886" author="lehmi" created="Sun, 18 Dec 2011 15:53:02 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;The compression type might get lost when setting the compression mode to MODE_EXPLICIT. There was another problem when adding the resolution to the metadata. &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I fixed that in revision 1220438.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I also added a unit test using PNG, JPG, BMP and WBMP as target format. GIF isn&apos;t supported as JDK 5 doesn&apos;t provide write support for it.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Thanks for the report!&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
